# v0.22.0 — Python content engine. Lives in this repo as a sibling package
# (per docs/content-engine-response.md § 1) but does NOT deploy to Vercel.
# It runs locally + via Cloudflare Workers / GitHub Actions per spec § 10.
#
# Vercel Build Inference scans the upload tree for pyproject.toml / *.py
# and tries to build a Python project — even when framework is set to
# "vite" in vercel.json. So we exclude the Python tree aggressively here:
# directory + every conceivable Python marker file. Belt-and-suspenders.
packages
packages/
packages/**
**/pyproject.toml
**/setup.py
**/requirements*.txt
**/*.py
spec-content-agent.md
